    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ISA 33:13" />¶ <char style="w" strong="H8085">Hear</char>, ye <char style="add">that are</char> far <char style="w" strong="H7350">off</char>, what I have <char style="w" strong="H6213">done</char>; and, ye <char style="add">that are</char> <char style="w" strong="H7138">near</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3045">acknowledge</char> my <char style="w" strong="H1369">might</char>. <verse eid="ISA 33:13" /><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ISA 33:14" />The <char style="w" strong="H2400">sinners</char> in <char style="w" strong="H6726">Zion</char> are <char style="w" strong="H6342">afraid</char>; <char style="w" strong="H7461">fearfulness</char> hath <char style="w" strong="H0270">surprised</char> the <char style="w" strong="H2611">hypocrites</char>. Who among us shall <char style="w" strong="H1481">dwell</char> with the <char style="w" strong="H0398">devouring</char> <char style="w" strong="H0784">fire</char>? who among us shall <char style="w" strong="H1481">dwell</char> with <char style="w" strong="H5769">everlasting</char> <char style="w" strong="H4168">burnings</char>? <verse eid="ISA 33:14" /><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ISA 33:15" />He that <char style="w" strong="H1980">walketh</char> <char style="w" strong="H6666">righteously</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H1696">speaketh</char> <char style="w" strong="H4339">uprightly</char>; he that <char style="w" strong="H3988">despiseth</char> the <char style="w" strong="H1215">gain</char> of <char style="w" strong="H4642">oppressions</char>, that <char style="w" strong="H5287">shaketh</char> his <char style="w" strong="H3709">hands</char> from <char style="w" strong="H8551">holding</char> of <char style="w" strong="H7810">bribes</char>, that <char style="w" strong="H0331">stoppeth</char> his <char style="w" strong="H0241">ears</char> from <char style="w" strong="H8085">hearing</char> of <char style="w" strong="H1818">blood</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H6105">shutteth